          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ", it could be the carrot which helps get the right person talking. The sports car belongs to Dennis’ brother Anthony. The family says in addition to the $10,000 they’re pledging to give an extra $500 a month for a year to the person who comes forward with information to put Gilliam’s murderer away.",
